57
00:05:40,966 --> 00:05:44,438
<i>Solo per te</i>

58
00:05:44,928 --> 00:05:47,443
<i>Senti</i>

59
00:05:47,529 --> 00:05:50,682
<i>Con quanto amore</i>

60
00:05:50,771 --> 00:05:54,652
<i>Questo mio cuore</i>

61
00:05:54,733 --> 00:05:58,887
<i>Batte per te</i>

